TIMOTHY JORDAN: For more
information about ModCloth--

00:05:48.948 --> 00:05:51.940
and maybe we can put some
of your favorite blogs

00:05:51.940 --> 00:05:53.580
and blog posts in
the notes as well.

00:05:53.580 --> 00:05:54.200
SUSAN KOGER: Amazing.

